<div id="review_291084194" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/291084194" />
    <a title="Steve L" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5916003-steve-l"><img alt="Steve L" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/291084194?book_show_action=true">Mar 08, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Steve L" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Steve L" href="/user/show/5916003-steve-l">Steve L</a>
      </span>

          added it




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer291084194" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7303973286631360060">A Discovery of a Crappy Book. This book is terrible. Why oh why were the stupid witches discovered. Here is the plot:<br/><br/>Day One.<br/><br/>I went to the library. I am a witch; he is a vampire. I shouldn&apos;t love him. But he is so cold and I am so hot for him. I had lunch and did some yoga.<br/><br/>Day Two.<br/><br/>I went to the library. Some people may or may not have been there, and they may or may not have been magical. I am a witch; he is a vampire. I shouldn&apos;t love him. But he is so cold and I am so hot for him. I had lunch </span>
  <span id="freeText7303973286631360060" style="display:none">A Discovery of a Crappy Book. This book is terrible. Why oh why were the stupid witches discovered. Here is the plot:<br /><br />Day One.<br /><br />I went to the library. I am a witch; he is a vampire. I shouldn't love him. But he is so cold and I am so hot for him. I had lunch and did some yoga.<br /><br />Day Two.<br /><br />I went to the library. Some people may or may not have been there, and they may or may not have been magical. I am a witch; he is a vampire. I shouldn't love him. But he is so cold and I am so hot for him. I had lunch and did some yoga.<br /><br />Day Three.<br /><br />I went to the library. Some people may or may not have been there, and they may or may not have been magical. Today's book glowed when I touched it. I am a witch. He is a vampire. I shouldn't love him. But he is so cold and I am so hot for him. I had lunch and did some yoga.<br /><br />This is seriously like the first 200 pages of the book. The rest doesn't get any better.</span>
